    WHERE [l].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [c].[LangId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentPageId], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypesId], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsBayi], [c0].[IsBireysel], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[IsEndustri], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsGallery], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsInteral], [c0].[IsInterax], [c0].[IsIntersecure], [c0].[IsInterwall], [c0].[IsMap], [c0].[IsMimar], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsStatus], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[LoginCount], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeywords], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[OrjId1], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]

    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[ContentPageId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[DocumentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentPageId], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypesId], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsBayi], [c1].[IsBireysel], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsDeleted], [c1].[IsEndustri], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsGallery], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsInteral], [c1].[IsInterax], [c1].[IsIntersecure], [c1].[IsInterwall], [c1].[IsMap], [c1].[IsMimar], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsStatus], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[LoginCount], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeywords], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[OrjId1], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]

    WHERE [c1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[ContentPageId]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[ContentTypesId] = @__selecttype_0)

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[Code], [l].[CreaDate], [l].[CreaUser], [l].[IsDefault], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[IsStatus], [l].[LoginCount], [l].[ModDate], [l].[ModUser], [l].[Name], [l].[OrderNo]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[LangId] = [t0].[Id]

    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [t].[ContentPageId] = [t1].[Id]
INNER JOIN (

) AS [t2] ON [t].[ContentTypesId] = [t2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t3] ON [t].[Id] = [t3].[DocumentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c2].[Id], [c2].[BannerButtonText], [c2].[BannerText], [c2].[ButtonLink], [c2].[ButtonText], [c2].[ContentData], [c2].[ContentOrderNo], [c2].[ContentPageId], [c2].[ContentShort], [c2].[ContentTypesId], [c2].[CreaDate], [c2].[CreaUser], [c2].[Description], [c2].[ExternalLink], [c2].[FormTypeId], [c2].[IsActive], [c2].[IsBayi], [c2].[IsBireysel], [c2].[IsClick], [c2].[IsDeleted], [c2].[IsEndustri], [c2].[IsFooterMenu], [c2].[IsGallery], [c2].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c2].[IsHeaderMenu], [c2].[IsInteral], [c2].[IsInterax], [c2].[IsIntersecure], [c2].[IsInterwall], [c2].[IsMap], [c2].[IsMimar], [c2].[IsPublish], [c2].[IsSideMenu], [c2].[IsStatus], [c2].[LangId], [c2].[Link], [c2].[LoginCount], [c2].[MetaDescription], [c2].[MetaKeywords], [c2].[MetaTitle], [c2].[ModDate], [c2].[ModUser], [c2].[Name], [c2].[OrderNo], [c2].[OrjId], [c2].[OrjId1], [c2].[TemplateType], [c2].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c2]
    WHERE [c2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[ContentPageId]

) AS [t] ON [c].[LangId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentPageId], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypesId], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsBayi], [c0].[IsBireysel], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[IsEndustri], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsGallery], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsInteral], [c0].[IsInterax], [c0].[IsIntersecure], [c0].[IsInterwall], [c0].[IsMap], [c0].[IsMimar], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsStatus], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[LoginCount], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeywords], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[OrjId1], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[ContentPageId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[DocumentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentPageId], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypesId], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsBayi], [c1].[IsBireysel], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsDeleted], [c1].[IsEndustri], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsGallery], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsInteral], [c1].[IsInterax], [c1].[IsIntersecure], [c1].[IsInterwall], [c1].[IsMap], [c1].[IsMimar], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsStatus], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[LoginCount], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeywords], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[OrjId1], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
    WHERE [c1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[ContentPageId]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[ContentTypesId] = @__selecttype_0)

""SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[IsTanim], [s].[LangId], [s].[LoginCount], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[OrjId], [s].[ParentId], [s].[SpecType], [t].[Id], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[IsTanim], [t].[LangId], [t].[LoginCount], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[OrjId], [t].[ParentId], [t].[SpecType], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AttrValue], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[LangId], [t0].[LoginCount], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[OrjId], [t0].[SpecId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[ContentPageId], [t1].[ContentValue], [t1].[CreaDate], [t1].[CreaUser], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[IsStatus], [t1].[LangId], [t1].[LoginCount], [t1].[ModDate], [t1].[ModUser], [t1].[OrderNo], [t1].[SpecId]
FROM [Spec] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[CreaDate], [s0].[CreaUser], [s0].[IsDeleted], [s0].[IsStatus], [s0].[IsTanim], [s0].[LangId], [s0].[LoginCount], [s0].[ModDate], [s0].[ModUser], [s0].[Name], [s0].[OrderNo], [s0].[OrjId], [s0].[ParentId], [s0].[SpecType]
    FROM [Spec] AS [s0]
    WHERE [s0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[ParentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[AttrValue], [s1].[CreaDate], [s1].[CreaUser], [s1].[IsDeleted], [s1].[IsStatus], [s1].[LangId], [s1].[LoginCount], [s1].[ModDate], [s1].[ModUser], [s1].[OrderNo], [s1].[OrjId], [s1].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecAttr] AS [s1]
    WHERE [s1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [s].[Id] = [t0].[SpecId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[ContentPageId], [s2].[ContentValue], [s2].[CreaDate], [s2].[CreaUser], [s2].[IsDeleted], [s2].[IsStatus], [s2].[LangId], [s2].[LoginCount], [s2].[ModDate], [s2].[ModUser], [s2].[OrderNo], [s2].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecContentValue] AS [s2]
    WHERE [s2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[SpecId]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]"

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[ContentPageId], [s2].[ContentValue], [s2].[CreaDate], [s2].[CreaUser], [s2].[IsDeleted], [s2].[IsStatus], [s2].[LangId], [s2].[LoginCount], [s2].[ModDate], [s2].[ModUser], [s2].[OrderNo], [s2].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecContentValue] AS [s2]
    WHERE [s2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[SpecId]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]"

LEFT JOIN (

FROM [Spec] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[CreaDate], [s0].[CreaUser], [s0].[IsDeleted], [s0].[IsStatus], [s0].[IsTanim], [s0].[LangId], [s0].[LoginCount], [s0].[ModDate], [s0].[ModUser], [s0].[Name], [s0].[OrderNo], [s0].[OrjId], [s0].[ParentId], [s0].[SpecType]
    FROM [Spec] AS [s0]
    WHERE [s0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[ParentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[AttrValue], [s1].[CreaDate], [s1].[CreaUser], [s1].[IsDeleted], [s1].[IsStatus], [s1].[LangId], [s1].[LoginCount], [s1].[ModDate], [s1].[ModUser], [s1].[OrderNo], [s1].[OrjId], [s1].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecAttr] AS [s1]
    WHERE [s1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [s].[Id] = [t0].[SpecId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[ContentPageId], [s2].[ContentValue], [s2].[CreaDate], [s2].[CreaUser], [s2].[IsDeleted], [s2].[IsStatus], [s2].[LangId], [s2].[LoginCount], [s2].[ModDate], [s2].[ModUser], [s2].[OrderNo], [s2].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecContentValue] AS [s2]
    WHERE [s2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[SpecId]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]"

) AS [t3]

""SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[IsTanim], [s].[LangId], [s].[LoginCount], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[OrjId], [s].[ParentId], [s].[SpecType], [t].[Id], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[IsTanim], [t].[LangId], [t].[LoginCount], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[OrjId], [t].[ParentId], [t].[SpecType], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AttrValue], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[LangId], [t0].[LoginCount], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[OrjId], [t0].[SpecId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[ContentPageId], [t1].[ContentValue], [t1].[CreaDate], [t1].[CreaUser], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[IsStatus], [t1].[LangId], [t1].[LoginCount], [t1].[ModDate], [t1].[ModUser], [t1].[OrderNo], [t1].[SpecId]
FROM [Spec] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[CreaDate], [s0].[CreaUser], [s0].[IsDeleted], [s0].[IsStatus], [s0].[IsTanim], [s0].[LangId], [s0].[LoginCount], [s0].[ModDate], [s0].[ModUser], [s0].[Name], [s0].[OrderNo], [s0].[OrjId], [s0].[ParentId], [s0].[SpecType]
    FROM [Spec] AS [s0]
    WHERE [s0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[ParentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[AttrValue], [s1].[CreaDate], [s1].[CreaUser], [s1].[IsDeleted], [s1].[IsStatus], [s1].[LangId], [s1].[LoginCount], [s1].[ModDate], [s1].[ModUser], [s1].[OrderNo], [s1].[OrjId], [s1].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecAttr] AS [s1]
    WHERE [s1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [s].[Id] = [t0].[SpecId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[ContentPageId], [s2].[ContentValue], [s2].[CreaDate], [s2].[CreaUser], [s2].[IsDeleted], [s2].[IsStatus], [s2].[LangId], [s2].[LoginCount], [s2].[ModDate], [s2].[ModUser], [s2].[OrderNo], [s2].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecContentValue] AS [s2]
    WHERE [s2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[SpecId]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]"

        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]

        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[BannerImageId]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_0)
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]

    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[DocumentId]

""SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[IsTanim], [s].[LangId], [s].[LoginCount], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[OrjId], [s].[ParentId], [s].[SpecType], [t].[Id], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[IsTanim], [t].[LangId], [t].[LoginCount], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[OrjId], [t].[ParentId], [t].[SpecType], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AttrValue], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[LangId], [t0].[LoginCount], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[OrjId], [t0].[SpecId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[ContentPageId], [t1].[ContentValue], [t1].[CreaDate], [t1].[CreaUser], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[IsStatus], [t1].[LangId], [t1].[LoginCount], [t1].[ModDate], [t1].[ModUser], [t1].[OrderNo], [t1].[SpecId]
FROM [Spec] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[CreaDate], [s0].[CreaUser], [s0].[IsDeleted], [s0].[IsStatus], [s0].[IsTanim], [s0].[LangId], [s0].[LoginCount], [s0].[ModDate], [s0].[ModUser], [s0].[Name], [s0].[OrderNo], [s0].[OrjId], [s0].[ParentId], [s0].[SpecType]
    FROM [Spec] AS [s0]
    WHERE [s0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[ParentId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s1].[Id], [s1].[AttrValue], [s1].[CreaDate], [s1].[CreaUser], [s1].[IsDeleted], [s1].[IsStatus], [s1].[LangId], [s1].[LoginCount], [s1].[ModDate], [s1].[ModUser], [s1].[OrderNo], [s1].[OrjId], [s1].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecAttr] AS [s1]
    WHERE [s1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [s].[Id] = [t0].[SpecId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s2].[Id], [s2].[ContentPageId], [s2].[ContentValue], [s2].[CreaDate], [s2].[CreaUser], [s2].[IsDeleted], [s2].[IsStatus], [s2].[LangId], [s2].[LoginCount], [s2].[ModDate], [s2].[ModUser], [s2].[OrderNo], [s2].[SpecId]
    FROM [SpecContentValue] AS [s2]
    WHERE [s2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[SpecId]
WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id]"
